25// tls1_prf calculates |out_len| bytes of the TLS PDF, using |digest|, and
26// writes them to |out|. It returns one on success and zero on error.
27OPENSSL_EXPORT int CRYPTO_tls1_prf(const EVP_MD *digest,
28 uint8_t *out, size_t out_len,
29 const uint8_t *secret, size_t secret_len,
30 const char *label, size_t label_len,
31 const uint8_t *seed1, size_t seed1_len,
32 const uint8_t *seed2, size_t seed2_len);
